snippet.title: Curiosity of a Turnabout! [BLIND] Part 1: A Tale Of SPELLs
snippet.description:
[A Visual Novelty]

We're playing a Blackrune fancase today, an apocalyptic future scenario where humans develop extraordinary powers called SPELLs, and strange alien creatures have rendered life outside the walls almost entirely untenable. In this world where lawyers have become unnecessary, a scientist has been asked to represent a client as a lawyer...

A Blackrune fancase! Play it here: http://aaonline.fr/player.php?trial_id=84718
